
GO TO The Administration Section

      > Click on "Add New User":

      
      > Enter the Username and Password
      Note: The Password must be more than 8 characters.
      
      
      > Enter the Password again in the Password Confirmation field
      
      
      > SAVE
      
Another page will open automatically;
      > Now enter the Personal info (first name, last name, etc)
      
      
      > Tick ALL the three fields (Active, Staff Status, Superuser)
      
      
      > CHOOSE only ONE choice in the GROUPS Section
      
      
      > DON'T TOUCH the User Permissions section - Leave it as it is.
      
      
      > SAVE
